entries.s_fa22e207: I would like to enter Deep Space!
entries.s_c4588d4d: I want to go to Kessel
entries.s_a99b5897: This area of Deep Space has been closed by order of the Empire.  The only way to get in is to pose as either an Imperial yourself, or to use the Rebel Alliance's hyperspace route.  Be warned though, whichever route you choose, you will be treated as an enemy by the other side!
entries.s_a785faa6: Which side would you like to support?
entries.s_7e6edae: This will cost %DI points of prestige.  Do you wish to spend the points and enter?
entries.s_3b257674: You need to move close to this station, %TU.
entries.s_37d359a2: You do not have enough Prestige to enter Deep Space.  You need %DI points.
entries.s_3693fe50: There's nothing we can do for you as long as you're in that civilian ship.
entries.s_11e15256: Ha ha!  I don't blame you.  Goodbye, then.
